		"civilopediaText": [
			{"text": "The Dwarven Kingdom of old was prosperous and full of splendor and glory. The majority of the Dwarven strongholds have fallen, one by one, in the bitter wars with the Orcs, Goblins or Skaven, even now the remaining few Dwarf cities are under constant siege. These centuries of war have hardened the Dwarfs and moulded them into some of the finest warriors of the Old World. Always a stubborn race, the Dwarfs still cling to what remains of their Kingdom, and dream of one day reclaiming their own (and extracting a terrible vengeance!)"},
