			{"text": "The ancient realm of Nehekhara was once the greatest civilisation of Men in the world, but hundreds of years before the rise of Sigmar the treachery of the Great Necromancer, Nagash, almost destroyed and enslaved this mighty realm. Brought back to immortal unlife by arcane magic, the Tomb Kings of Nehekhara continue to lead their Undead armies, fighting to protect their mighty empire from the depredations of the lesser races and expand their dominion even further."},
